39:["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Yes, and for larger businesses we recommend bringing the team member most responsible for operations. Having the right people in the room produces a more accurate and actionable Blueprint. We recommend a maximum of 3 people from your side to keep the session focused."}]}]
3a:["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-group","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"faq-group-label","children":"About the Engagement"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["How long does implementation take?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Typically 4–10 weeks depending on scope and complexity. A focused engagement covering 3–4 core systems usually runs 4–6 weeks. A full operating system covering every business function can take 8–12 weeks. The Blueprint gives you the exact timeline for your specific project."}]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["Can you integrate with my existing tech stack?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Almost always, yes. We assess your current tools during the Blueprint and design around them wherever possible. We only recommend replacements when a tool is genuinely creating more friction than value. We do not push specific platforms."}]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["Do you work with international clients?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Yes. All engagements are conducted remotely via video. We work with clients across North America, Europe, Africa, the Middle East and Asia-Pacific. Sessions are scheduled to accommodate your timezone."}]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["How much does implementation cost?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"We do not publish fixed pricing because every engagement is scoped to your specific business. Most projects range from $3,500 for focused single-system builds to $20,000+ for comprehensive operating system implementations. The Blueprint includes an exact investment estimate for your project. The $500 Blueprint fee is credited in full if you proceed."}]}]]}]]]}]
3b:["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-group","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"faq-group-label","children":"About Fit"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["What if I'm already using some AI tools?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Good — that gives us a foundation to build on. Having individual AI tools is very different from having an AI Operating System. Most clients we work with have already tried ChatGPT, Zapier or various AI writing tools. The problem is those tools aren't connected into a coherent system. That is precisely what we design and build."}]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["Who is this NOT for?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"This is not for you if: you are in the very early stages of business with no established processes yet (you need processes before you can systematize them); you are looking for a cheap solution or want to spend less than $3,500 on implementation; you want someone to hand you a tool and disappear; you are not willing to invest time in the Blueprint process and preparation; or you do not believe AI has a role in your business model. There is no judgment in any of these — this specific service just will not deliver the right outcome for you."}]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["Do I need technical knowledge?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"No. You need to understand your business — the flows, the bottlenecks, the decisions you make every day. We handle all technical design and implementation. Most of our clients describe themselves as \"not technical.\" What matters is operational clarity, not coding skills."}]}]]}]]]}]
3c:["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-group","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"faq-group-label","children":"About Outcomes"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["What does success look like 90 days after implementation?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Typically: 6–12 hours per week recovered from operational tasks. Client-facing processes running without your personal involvement. A knowledge base your team can access without asking you. Fewer dropped balls. Less reactive decision-making. The specific outcomes depend on your business and what we build — the Blueprint will define the exact success metrics for your situation."}]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["What is the AI Optimization Partnership?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"A monthly ongoing relationship for clients who want their AI OS to evolve with their business. It includes: monthly system improvements and new automations, prompt optimization as AI models update, performance monitoring, quarterly strategy sessions, team training as needed, and priority access for new requests. It is not maintenance. It is active optimization."}]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["What if I need changes or additions after implementation?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"Small adjustments within scope are handled during implementation at no additional cost. Significant new additions or new systems are scoped as separate projects. The AI Optimization Partnership includes ongoing small improvements as standard. Your operating system should evolve — we build for that from the start."}]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"className":"faq-item","children":[["$","button",null,{"className":"faq-question","aria-expanded":"false","children":["How do you measure ROI?",["$","svg",null,{"className":"faq-question-icon","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","fill":"none","aria-hidden":"true","children":["$","path",null,{"d":"M8 3v10M3 8h10","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"1.3","strokeLinecap":"round"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"faq-answer-inner","children":"We define success metrics during the Blueprint and track them through implementation. Primary metrics include: hours recovered per week (and the dollar value of that time), reduction in operational errors, client response time improvement, team hours saved, and revenue per founder hour. The ROI opportunity map delivered with your Blueprint quantifies the expected return before you commit to implementation."}]}]]}]]]}]
